aboutMeText:
I am Brazilian, I have a degree in computer science and I have about age of experience as a programmer.

I am a fullstack developer, mainly focused on .NET Core (C#) and platforms with Javascript/Typescript such as Angular, Vue, Stencil and React.

I have worked on several projects in various areas, the biggest ones were:

- Mapfre, in the insurance and capitalization system;
- Banco Safra, in the open banking and loans system;
- Motiva, URA system (automatic call robot);

I have advanced English for both writing and conversation.
